DATA PIPELINE IMPLEMENTATIONS:

  src/pipeline/sources.py
    YFinancePriceSource(IPriceSource)
      fetch() handles batching retry and rate limiting
      batch_size retry_count retry_wait rate_limit from settings
      never raises on individual ticker failure
      logs failures returns available tickers only

  src/pipeline/cache.py
    ParquetCache(ICache)
      read() write() exists() get_last_date()
      key maps to parquet filepath under settings.raw_dir
      get_last_date() reads last index value from parquet

  src/pipeline/downloader.py
    IncrementalDownloader
      depends on IPriceSource and ICache via constructor
      on first run fetches full history
      on subsequent runs fetches only since get_last_date()
      appends new data to existing cache
      writes download_meta.json after each run
      does not know whether source is yfinance or anything else

  src/pipeline/cleaner.py
    StandardCleaner(IDataCleaner)
      forward fill maximum 5 consecutive days
      drop ticker if fewer than min_history_pct trading days
      drop ticker if average price below min_price
      log anomalies to anomaly_log.csv do not drop them
      anomaly threshold absolute return > 0.25

  src/pipeline/returns.py
    LogReturnsProcessor(IReturnsProcessor)
      np.log(prices / prices.shift(1)).dropna()

    WeeklyResampleProcessor(IReturnsProcessor)
      decorator wrapping another IReturnsProcessor
      applies prices.resample("W-FRI").last() first
      then delegates to wrapped processor
      used for global model only
      open for extension without modifying LogReturnsProcessor

  src/pipeline/threshold.py
    VolatilityThresholdStrategy(IThresholdStrategy)
      threshold_multiplier times mean of per-stock std
      multiplier from settings

    FixedThresholdStrategy(IThresholdStrategy)
      returns fixed value from settings
      used when user overrides auto threshold

  src/pipeline/pairs.py
    CoMovementPairGenerator(IPairGenerator)
      up bucket return > threshold
      down bucket return < negative threshold
      all combinations within each bucket
      bidirectional A-B and B-A both added
      cap at max_pairs_per_day random sample if exceeded

  src/pipeline/status.py
    TrainingStatus
      write_status(market, mode, epoch, total_epochs,
                   loss, started_at)
      write_complete(market, final_loss, validation_results)
      write_failed(market, error_message)
      read_status(market) -> dict
      write_reload_signal(market, version)
      check_reload_signal(market) -> bool

