      initialise() random W1 W2 with seed
      forward() returns h scores probs
      backward() returns dW2 dh
        CRITICAL: dscores[target_idx] -= 1 never = -1
        loss variable not computed here
        loss computed in Trainer for monitoring only
      update() applies lr * gradient to W1 row and W2
      get_embeddings() returns W1 copy

  src/training/observers.py
    LossCsvObserver(ITrainingObserver)
      on_epoch_end() appends epoch and avg_loss to CSV
      single responsibility: CSV loss logging only

    StatusFileObserver(ITrainingObserver)
      on_epoch_end() calls TrainingStatus.write_status()
      on_training_complete() calls write_complete()
      on_error() calls write_failed()
      single responsibility: status file only

    CheckpointObserver(ITrainingObserver)
      on_checkpoint() saves W1 npy file to checkpoints/
      only fires every checkpoint_every_epochs
      single responsibility: checkpoint saving only

    DashboardNotifierObserver(ITrainingObserver)
      on_training_complete() calls write_reload_signal()
      single responsibility: notify dashboard only

  src/training/lr_strategy.py
    ScanLRStrategy(ILRStrategy)
      tests each value in lr_scan_values for lr_scan_epochs
      selects largest where final loss < starting loss
      logs selected lr

    FixedLRStrategy(ILRStrategy)
      returns fixed lr from settings

  src/training/clipping.py
    GradientClipper(IGradientClipper)
      np.clip(gradient, -clip_value, clip_value)
      clip_value from settings

  src/training/stopping.py
