THREE TRAINING MODES:

  full retrain:
    random initialisation full date range
    refresh dynamic universe from Wikipedia
    triggers S3 backup after validation passes

  incremental update:
    load existing weights continue training
    new data only since last_trained_date
    no vocab changes

  fine-tune recent window:
    load existing weights finetune_window_days of data
    lr multiplied by finetune_lr_multiplier
    no vocab changes

TRAINING LOOP REQUIREMENTS:
  shuffle pairs each epoch
  compute loss for monitoring log to CSV do not use in update
  update training_status.json after every epoch
  checkpoint W1 every checkpoint_every_epochs
  checkpoint filename W1_epoch_{n:04d}.npy
  early stop if loss increases for early_stop_patience epochs
  gradient clipping applied before every weight update

TRAINING STATUS FILE:
  data/models/{market}/training_status.json
  status field: idle running complete failed
  updated every epoch during training
  full schema defined in Section 16

MODEL VERSIONING:
  directory: data/models/{market}/v{n}_{YYYYMMDD}_{mode}/
  W1.npy as float32 vocab.json metadata.json
  loss_history.csv validation.json checkpoints/
  current/ updated ONLY after validation passes
  reload_signal.json written after current/ updated

TRAINING ORDER:
  US then NZX then ASX then Global always

